The Authority is seeking via a competitive dialogue tender process a development partner to lead the residential development of the Maidenhead Golf Course. The Authority's objectives are:
- To promote the site for residential allocation in anticipation of the Local Plan Examination;
- Assemble any parts of the site outside of the control of the Authority;
- Secure a development partner that will invest in the project and generate a financial return for the Authority; - To deliver a comprehensive residential led redevelopment of circa 2 000 homes together with affordable housing;
- At the option of the Authority to introduce to the opportunity additional land in connection with the proposed redevelopment beyond the boundary of Maidenhead Golf Course itself.
